    How To Buy

    HOW TO BUY

    Create a Wallet

    Download the OKX app from the App Store or Google Play Store for free. Once installed, create an account and complete the KYC process to activate your wallet.

    Get Some ETH

    Make sure you have ETH in your OKX Web3 wallet to swap for GUA. If you don’t have any ETH, you can purchase it directly within the OKX app, transfer from another wallet, or buy on an exchange and send it to your OKX Web3 wallet.

    Trade in OKX Web3 Wallet

    Open your OKX Web3 wallet and click the "Trade" button. Paste the GUA token address: 0x393f1D49425d94f47b26E591a9D111df5cD61065 into the token search bar, select GUA, and confirm the trade. When OKX prompts you for a wallet signature, sign it to complete the process.

    Switch ETH for $GUA

    Swap your ETH for GUA. GUA is designed with ZERO taxes, so you don’t need to worry about setting a specific slippage. However, during times of market volatility, you might need to adjust the slippage slightly.
